overview: "Musse The Movie" is full of high performance surfing starring some of the best surfers in Brazil, highlighting Neco Padaratz, Fabio Gouveia, Jean da Silva, Willian Cardoso, Tiago Bianchini, Tomas Hermes, Mickey Bernardoni, Petterson Thomaz, Heitor Alves, Caetano Vargas and Rafael Imhof among others destroying, making fun of and enjoying the best Beach Breaks in Brazil and some beaches around the world. "Musse The Movie" has approximately 40 minutes, edited in a nervous and frenetic language, focusing on modern maneuvers accompanied by a heavy and consistent soundtrack.
title: Musse The Movie
